    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine currently struggles to stay idle and exhibits a noticeable knock, while the transmission shifts harshly between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several deep scratches and dents along the passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional air conditioning. It is recommended for a buyer looking for a project car or a source for parts, as it is currently not reliable for daily transportation.",
      "price": 4800.0,
